Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个风雨交加的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A dark and stormy night
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.06,0:01:08.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正是这样的夜晚令我回想起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:08.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's nights like these that remind me of
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.06,0:01:10.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前有一刻  蟹老板与海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:10.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the time Mr. Krabs and SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,误以为自己杀了个卫生检查员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:12.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thought they killed a health inspector
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.15,0:01:16.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是一个晴朗的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:16.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a bright and sunny morning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:19.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(312,316)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:21.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(510,764)}卫生检查员
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那味道好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That smells like
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卫生检查员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the health inspector
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.59,0:01:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去洗手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wash your hands
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.65,0:01:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打扫地板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,clean the floors
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.62,0:01:32.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换掉内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:32.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,change your underwear
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卫生检查员来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The health inspector's here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是他找到一处卫生不合格的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If he finds one health violation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.51,0:01:38.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会让我们永远关门大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:38.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he'll close us down for good
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.20,0:01:41.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们必须得尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:41.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to do everything in our power
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确保他能让蟹堡王合格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make sure he passes the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.95,0:01:45.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:45.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to worry
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.92,0:01:50.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王是全宇宙最完美的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:48.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:50.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the most perfect place in the universe
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.06,0:01:53.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是根本就没脑子  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:53.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really haven't got any brains at all, have you, son?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.79,0:01:56.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去给他需要的东西就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:56.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just go out there and give him what he needs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.85,0:01:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去献殷勤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pour on the charm
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多说好话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet talk him
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I get for you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.66,0:02:03.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:03.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,handsome?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.49,0:02:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.08,0:02:09.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菜单上的所有东西都给我拿一份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need you to bring me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:09.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one of everything on the menu
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.46,0:02:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选得好  爱人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excellent choice, my darling
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming right up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要所有东西都来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wants one of everything
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那咱就给他来份自助大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then we'll give him a smorgasbord
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王未来的成败在此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The future of the Krusty Krab is at stake
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝尝蟹堡王海草热狗吧  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try the Krusty Kelp Dog, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄油藤壶能让你感受天堂的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Buttered Barnacles are a touch of heaven
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浮木粉味美可口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Powdered Driftwood is exquisite
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新鲜淤泥布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fresh Sludge Pudding?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.14,0:02:27.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,低糖赤潮还要不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:27.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More Diet Red Tide?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.06,0:02:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,油炸船只残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some Fried Flotsam?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打住  先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要一个人安安静静完成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave me to finish my work in peace
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.38,0:02:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位丰满的检查员用餐可否愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And did the voluptuous inspector enjoy his meal?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目前还行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So far, so good
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.44,0:02:45.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要再吃一个原味蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:45.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just need to try a plain Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.49,0:02:47.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能完成检查了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:47.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and my inspection will be finished
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.91,0:02:50.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说只要再来一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:50.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He says if he gets one more Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能让我们检查合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he'll pass us for the inspection
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道这什么意思吗  亲爱的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means, dear boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们过关了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're in the clear
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.55,0:03:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要打断这场康康舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We interrupt this can-can
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,插播一则特别简讯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a special news bulletin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:08.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(394,584)}裤头村新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.83,0:03:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请各位注意一名为了吃霸王餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be on the lookout for a man
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who's been passing himself off
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而伪装成卫生检查员的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as a health inspector in order to obtain free food
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.64,0:03:09.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以上就是全部内容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:09.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's all for now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.48,0:03:15.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,霸王餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:15.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free food?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能该要跟那位提一提假检查员的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we oughta tell our guy about the phony impostor
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个白痴  那位就是假检查员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You loony loofah, he is the impostor
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been duped
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Duped?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.07,0:03:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,受骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bamboozled
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们上骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been smeckledorfed
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那根本就不算话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not even a word
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.41,0:03:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I agree with ya
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看人家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at him
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他内裤肯定从来都没换
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet he never changes his underpants
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他肯定咬过鲸鱼吐的泡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet he bites whale bubbles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那帽子肯定是他妈给他买的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet his mom bought him that hat
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果说那个冒牌货要蟹黄堡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If that impostor wants a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.55,0:03:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那以海神王的名义  直接成全他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then by Neptune, we'll give him one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:43.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678,374)}火山辣酱
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在是在与蟹共舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're dancin' with the crab man now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.40,0:03:47.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我一起干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:47.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Join me, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or you're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样好像不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过特别的爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it feels so good
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海马辣根酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seahorse radish
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底最呛的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the gnarliest stuff in the ocean
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.94,0:04:00.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  我办公室里有罐脚趾甲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:04:00.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I've got a jar of toenail clippings in my office
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把它给掉马桶里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I dropped it in the toilet
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.90,0:04:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就捞出来  我要拿运动袜来擦干它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, fish it out, and I'll dry it with me gym socks
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.47,0:04:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是史上最恶心的蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, that's the most diabolical
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty ever spawned
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我管这叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏的汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Nasty Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧把蟹黄堡送上来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with that patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.76,0:04:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生给  请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you are, sir, enjoy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  美味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到爸爸这来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to papa
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快听  他吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, he ate it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看把人家给噎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at him choke
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看人家那疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at him suffer
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you see that, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他脸上那表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That look on his face
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们打断你们的幸灾乐祸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We interrupt your laughter at other people's expense
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,插播本则新闻快讯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to bring you this news flash
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假检查员已经被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fake inspector has been captured
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,590)}裤头村新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是他的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here is his picture
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果有个卫生检查员光顾你的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If a health inspector comes to your restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且也不是这位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he's not this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's real
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下放心了  对吧蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a relief, eh, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.05,0:05:21.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要把情况解释清楚  他肯定会理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure our guy will understand
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if we just explain the situation
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后大家就能一笑了之了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then we can all have a good laugh about it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他多半笑不出来了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think he'll be laughin', boy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为那汉堡把他给害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because that patty killed him
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我们要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.86,0:05:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this "we" stuff?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏的汉堡是你给他吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fed him the tainted patty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.08,0:05:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你得坐牢去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's the stony lonesome for you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是是你要我给他吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you told me to give it to him
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你本来不是可以阻止我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you could've talked me out of it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm guilty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在监狱里绝对活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never survive in prison
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会被拿来拖地的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll mop up the floor with me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静点  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get ahold of yourself, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁没人看见  赶紧处理掉这具尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to get rid of this body before anyone sees it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得要把他带出去埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to take it out and bury it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好恶心  好多细菌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gross, germs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黏糊糊的  还死气沉沉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all icky and corpse-y
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边应该够远了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This should be far enough
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.28,0:06:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在开始挖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get diggin'
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.34,0:06:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下面磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the holdup down there?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有块大石头挡住路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:26.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a big rock in the way
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就扔出去继续挖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, toss it out and get back to diggin'
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这是在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有哪里不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somethin' ain't quite right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他头还露在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His head's stickin' out
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.52,0:06:47.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为得帮他透气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:47.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought he might need some air
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去阴间用不着空气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't need air where he's going
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就不该为他说几句悼词吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we say a few words on his behalf?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他为全世界的卫生检查员带来了荣光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was a credit to health inspectors everywhere, and
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.74,0:06:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多么勇敢无畏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a brave man
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.91,0:07:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果却因公殉职了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,going in the line of duty like that
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.24,0:07:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  你个呆头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen here, ya little barnacle
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.29,0:07:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且谁都不准知道有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I mean no one can ever know about this
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你就完了  我就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll be the end of you, it'll be the end of me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And worst of all
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll be the end of me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都待在那不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop right where you are
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕我们得要逮捕你们两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we're going to have to arrest the two of you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我年纪轻轻不能坐牢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I'm too young to go to jail
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.93,0:07:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们犯了什么罪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what would be the charges?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罪名是你们没有待在蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For not being at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.23,0:07:28.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我们做几份好吃的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:28.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to whip us up a couple of dee-licious Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laugh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把那泥铲子放后备箱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put that muddy shovel in the trunk
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们开车送你们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we'll give you a ride back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, listen carefully
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是要搭便车回蟹堡王去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're just getting a lift back to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.79,0:08:03.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要冷静别慌张  懂不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you to stay calm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and don't lose your cool, understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我能慌张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I lose my cool now?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.25,0:08:06.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:06.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把他放后备箱里  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put him in the trunk, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去拖住警察
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll keep them cops busy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面是在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the holdup back there?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.28,0:08:17.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:17.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快起开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.92,0:08:24.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:24.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后面可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All set back here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后备箱那个沾满泥的铲子正常得很
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing unusual about a muddy shovel in the trunk
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.05,0:08:31.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:31.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All set
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You okay there, little fella?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他很容易晕车的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He gets carsick real easy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就系好安全带  我们会稳点开的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, buckle up and we'll drive real smooth-like
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.02,0:08:47.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:47.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now listen, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我们到了蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When we get to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.01,0:08:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要你带着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to take
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个铲子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that shovel
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.73,0:08:54.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把人家拉到什么后门之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:54.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and bring it around to the back entrance and stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.38,0:08:54.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:54.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放到冰库里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stow it in the freezer
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你懂不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我懂是懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I understand, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是你要我怎么处理那个死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but what do you want me to do with the bo
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.51,0:09:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苏打水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ttles of soda
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.93,0:09:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几罐苏打水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bottles of soda
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一回事  都放冰库里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Same thing, put 'em in the freezer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1124,704)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.64,0:09:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, man
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is so gross
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后门给锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The back door is locked
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy there, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是还在那外头处理那铲子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you were out back taking care of that shovel
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后门给锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the back door was locked
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就到这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I came around here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So if you'll excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去把我帽子放冰库里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go put my hat in the freezer now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okey-dokey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那小子没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that kid okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.33,0:09:49.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他行为有点诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:49.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's actin' a little funny
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(720,920)}诡 异
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.21,0:09:51.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:51.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他啊  老好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a real cut-up, that one
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他很会让大伙儿笑口常开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He knows how to keep the crew in stitches
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太搞笑了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.80,0:09:57.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他啊  老是戏多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:57.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always on, that one
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他那逗趣开关就是关不动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no off on his funny switch
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.85,0:10:03.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:03.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是  真是笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're, you're killin' me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.48,0:10:12.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  我差点给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:12.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, I almost forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在是开收银机撒钱夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Open Cash Register Night
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.48,0:10:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前两名顾客能获得收银机里所有的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First two customers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get all the money in the cash register
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡先不要了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,86 those patties, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.77,0:10:27.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚接到报警
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:27.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just got a call
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说是有两个变态在浅坟路埋尸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about two ghouls burying a stiff
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,over by Shallow Grave Road
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.45,0:10:31.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来杯汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:31.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a soda
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.87,0:10:32.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汽水给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:32.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your soda
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为警官们服务是我一大荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always a pleasure to serve the folks in blue
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, goodbye now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有加冰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no ice
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.81,0:10:39.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要冰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:39.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want ice?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的想要冰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want, you want ice?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.30,0:10:42.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:42.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要我做的黑暗勾当已完成  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The dark deed you requested is done, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get it myself
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰就在冰库里面  对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice is in the freezer, ri?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有冰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is no ice
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面从来就没有冰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's never been any ice
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.81,0:10:51.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰都是传说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:51.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice is just a myth
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step aside
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们搞得好像犯了谋杀案一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You people act like you've committed a murder
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.44,0:10:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.48,0:10:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我全招了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I confess
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是海绵宝宝杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob killed him
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.11,0:11:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不可以让我背黑锅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't pin this whole rap on me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他疯掉了  还失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He was insane, out of control
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.07,0:11:05.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一你们俩没来  他也会杀掉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:05.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He would've killed me too if you two hadn't come along
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是蟹老板主谋的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all Mr. Krabs' idea
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快抓住他  他就一疯狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put him down now, he's a mad dog
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他睡觉还戴卷发夹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wears curlers to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.87,0:11:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you two talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们杀了个卫生检查员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We killed a health inspector
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,埋了人家  还把他尸体放冰库里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buried him and then stuffed his body in the freezer
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说这里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.16,0:11:25.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:25.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's empty?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是不是在开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of a joke?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A joke
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能他变成丧尸走出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, maybe he turned into a zombie and walked out
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丧尸来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the zombie
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.47,0:11:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃我这招  你个丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that, you zombie
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take it from here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丧尸去死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Die, zombie
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  南希警官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good police work, Officer Nancy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位不是丧尸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy's not a zombie
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.27,0:12:03.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是一普普通通的卫生检查员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:03.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's just an ordinary health inspector
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.72,0:12:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要冒着再次被打的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And at the risk of being hit again
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你们这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to present you with this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1222,198)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1166,666)}合格
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, look
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们检查合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We passed the inspection
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都快来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡五折优惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties at half price
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, not really
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊  我要来份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, I'd like a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,故事到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the story
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  他们应该都是白痴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are all idiots, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.64,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(363,347)}白痴盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,464)\frz18.67}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:38.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.67\pos(308,392)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.67\pos(388,274)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:40.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.67\pos(330,328)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:40.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.67\pos(490,662)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:40.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见什么东西了吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See anything yet, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.36,0:12:47.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得要戴眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:47.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need my glasses
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是邮车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the mail truck
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包裹来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our package
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道今天是快乐跳跳傻子节
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize it was Happy Hopping Moron Day
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好大的盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a big box
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.37,0:13:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么时候可以不跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When do we stop hopping?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再等三十秒  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thirty more seconds, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.04,0:13:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们怕是订了一辈子用不完的泡泡皂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:19.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They probably ordered
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a lifetime supply of bubble soap
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新款电视
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A brand-new television?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.98,0:13:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.73,0:13:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来我还以为他们傻到不能再傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just when I thought they couldn't get any stupider
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把事情弄清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me get this straight
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个订了台大屏幕电视
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you two ordered a giant screen television
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是为了玩这个盒子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just so you could play in the box?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很聪明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty smart, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来以为没法用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought it wouldn't work
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真不走寻常路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's quite a plan there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.00,0:13:54.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是等下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:54.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But wait
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有事情要问你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There was something else I wanted to ask you two
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what was it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.92,0:14:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个是不是没脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you two have any brains?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我们不需要电视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, we don't need television
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只需要有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not as long as we have our
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还真没这么想过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought of it that way
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's really something
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能拿你们电视走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have your TV?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.12,0:14:19.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:19.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想当什么就当什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can be anything I want
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.22,0:14:27.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当橄榄球球员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:27.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A football player
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当海星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A starfish
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你本来就已经是海星了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're already a starfish
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象力有用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It works
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.18,0:14:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You try
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好  我来想象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想象我在看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm imaging myself watching TV
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电视就出现在那了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and there it is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能拿吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I have it, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.57,0:14:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.57,0:14:47.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是改主意  我们就待这盒子里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:47.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if you change your mind, we'll be in this box
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来玩爬山大冒险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's play Mountain Climbing Adventure
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go for it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.47,0:14:53.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:53.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gloves
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.17,0:14:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.75,0:14:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hats
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.21,0:14:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Underwear
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.06,0:14:57.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:57.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.67,0:14:58.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:14:58.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬上去系好安全绳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Climb up there and secure this rope
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你爬得太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're going too high
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.69,0:15:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望他们给盒子开了通气口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope they put some air holes in that box
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放轻松  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得适应环境
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to acclimate
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我死了再放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:16.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take it easy when I'm dead
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在跟海神王握手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm shaking hands with Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精益求精
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excelsior
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.67,标准-Chi,,0,650,0,,遥控器哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:23.67,标准-Eng,,0,650,0,,Where's that remote?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是蜥蜴王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the lizard king
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要把声音放小点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we should keep our voices down
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.93,0:15:34.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然可能会引发雪崩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:34.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We might start an avalanche
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.43,0:15:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要把声音放小点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we should keep our voices down
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,防止出雪崩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in case of avalanches
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.93,0:15:43.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把什么放小点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:43.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should we keep down?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morons
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说话的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our voices
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you two shut up?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快抓紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撑住  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救援直升机马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The chopper's on the way
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.47,0:16:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我腿给冻僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My legs are frozen solid
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得拿锯子把我腿给锯掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have to cut them off with a saw
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.17,0:16:25.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:25.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.83,0:16:26.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:26.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.77,0:16:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我已经把我胳膊给割掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because I already cut off my own arms
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.24,0:16:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个咋发出来声音的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How were you two making that noise?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What noise, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只能听到我们发出来的笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could only hear the sound of our laughter
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.45,0:16:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是那些音效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But those sound effects
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有雪崩  跟跟跟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the avalanche, the, the, the
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.50,0:16:45.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二场雪崩别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:45.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the second avalanche
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.36,0:16:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道我干嘛要待外面浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I'm wasting my time out here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.63,0:16:55.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来这个时候我还可以看新款电视的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:55.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I could be watching my brand new television
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,登山者们请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, climbers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锯子马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The saws are on the way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are you doing that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先在海拔15000英尺的地方建大本营
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First we establish a base camp at 15,000 feet
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的是声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The noises
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个怎么发出的那些声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are you two making those noises?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要来个盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you need is a box
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是不是要说我没有想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say that I have no imagination?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.92,0:17:28.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我随便一根触手里掌握的想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:28.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have more imagination in one tentacle
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都比你们两个全身加起来的还多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than you two have in your whole bodies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's good
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只要有个盒子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all you need is a box
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒要给他们见识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show them
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面肯定有盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's got to be one in here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个帽子盒应该不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This hat box should do nicely
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么从来没戴过这帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why haven't I worn this yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have you surrounded
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,举起双手马上出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come out with your hands up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们找我干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do they want with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很明显我违反了新出的某种踢盒子法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Obviously I violated some new box-kicking law
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警官  你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, officers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次不犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.71,0:18:20.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不可能会活捉我的  警察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:20.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never take me alive, coppers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  约翰尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Johnny
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.64,0:18:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又有盒子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another box
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.77,0:18:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得好好放松
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to try to relax
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.90,0:18:38.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电视声应该能盖过他们的幼稚游戏声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I can drown out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,their childish games with a little TV
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.49,0:18:43.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,组装盒子的最后阶段就在此处完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is here that the boxes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,reach their final stage of assembly
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.95,0:18:47.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面这个盒子证明了这个方程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:47.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The equation is demonstrated here by this box
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今年买不起礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't afford a present this year
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我给你送了这个盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I got you this box
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也送的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I got you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.36,0:18:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就没一个跟盒子没关系的节目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything on that isn't about boxes?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.42,0:19:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回到拳击锦标赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:19:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And welcome back to Championship Boxing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:19:00.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(744,920)}盒 子
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这节目倒还好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess this is okay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.65,0:19:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少说跟盒子没多大关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not really about boxes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我服了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I give up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.85,0:19:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.66,0:19:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blast off
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are they doing that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我听过最真实的火箭发射声了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the most realistic space launch I ever heard
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定有什么能解释这现象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There must be an explanation
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  快想啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think, Squidward, think
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥好笨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's such a jerk
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘲笑我是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laugh at me, will they?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, where is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I am
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.58,0:19:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么在哪  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's what, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别拿同样的话回我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't "Where's what, Squidward?" me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.98,0:19:52.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,录音机在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:52.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the tape recorder?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有录音机  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't have a tape recorder, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.19,0:19:57.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别拿同样的话回我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:57.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't "We don't have a tape recorder, Squidward" me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们真没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we don't
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒是有个录音机盒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have a tape recorder box
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.69,0:20:01.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:01.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个让开  我要进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way, you two, I'm coming in
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎登船  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你登上的这艘船名叫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've just set sail on the S.S.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.99,0:20:10.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象力号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:10.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们唯一的目的地就是奇幻冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where our only destination is fantastic adventure
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要先去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go first?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.25,0:20:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用不着管我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就待这光看着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to observe
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是章鱼哥  你不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Squidward, don't you see?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待这光看着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waiting and watching?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不符合盒子的内在精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not what the box is about
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.82,0:20:26.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在精神在于
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:26.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's about
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.91,0:20:29.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:29.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好那好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, fine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.30,0:20:33.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带我去机器海盗岛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:33.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take me to Robot Pirate Island
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.04,0:20:36.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跟月球上的牛仔掰手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:36.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna arm-wrestle with cowboys on the moon
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.51,0:20:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧摔  这样我好回去看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just do it so I can get back and watch TV
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.16,0:20:43.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器海盗岛到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:43.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robot Pirate Island it is
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同伴好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy matey
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们犯了错  得走甲板落海去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For that you'll walk the plank
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.88,0:21:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意怎么就不打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why won't this thing turn on?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好那好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, fine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不给我看的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to show me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.21,0:21:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也就不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有更好的事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got better things to do
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.05,0:21:12.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不会走来走去想你们怎么操作的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:10.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than pace the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wondering how you two work this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.93,0:21:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那两个怎么操作的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do those two work that thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.07,0:21:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定有什么秘密按钮开关之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:16.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's got to be a secret button
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or a switch or something
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.62,0:21:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听人家的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, listen to that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.03,0:21:24.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就是机器海盗岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:24.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that sounds like Robot Pirate Island
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  快想啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think, Squidward, think
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.76,0:21:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到那两个上床睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When those two go to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.32,0:21:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就偷偷溜进去找按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll sneak in there and find that button
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.20,0:21:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等个一整晚我都愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll wait all night if I have to
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.80,0:21:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得睡一觉  给我的想象力加个油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need sleep to refuel my imagination tanks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.78,0:21:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是不敢相信海盗把机器人都打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,those pirates beat all those robots
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.05,0:21:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明早再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you in the morning
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.62,0:21:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.16,0:22:11.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:11.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, what's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.13,0:22:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谨以此牌匾纪念勇猛海盗们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.13,0:22:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This plaque is to commemorate the brave pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.87,0:22:15.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为安全护送该盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who gave their lives to keep this box
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.86,0:22:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免受机器人威胁而牺牲的壮举
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,safe from the Robot Menace
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.10,0:22:19.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远铭记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:19.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lest we forget
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.71,0:22:22.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得赶紧找按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:22.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to find that button quick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定就在这边哪个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's got to be around here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.32,0:22:25.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:25.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.68,0:22:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一空盒子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just an empty box
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.59,0:22:31.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能还真是他们的想象力弄出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:31.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it really was their imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.14,0:22:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it together, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.60,0:22:34.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:34.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我难道真的会相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, do I really believe that
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.39,0:22:39.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我坐这假装在开赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:39.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if I sit here and pretend to drive a race car
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.64,0:22:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我就突然会听到声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I'm suddenly going to start hearing noises?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.44,0:22:44.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:44.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真的有用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It actually works
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.24,0:22:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.49,0:22:51.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:51.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.34,0:22:53.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比电视强太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:53.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This beats TV by a long shot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:23:00.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(536,776)}垃圾
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.96,0:23:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我玩得最开心的一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the most fun I've ever had
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.36,0:23:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗快听
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen to that, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥可终于会用盒子了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward finally made the box work after all
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.27,0:23:07.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's so great
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:13.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,308)}垃圾场
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.72,0:23:16.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就差两圈就要到终点了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:16.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only two more laps to the finish line
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.39,0:23:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我领先
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in the lead
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.35,0:23:19.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:19.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of my way
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.29,0:23:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.29,0:23:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.27,0:23:24.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胜利属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:24.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Victory is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们盒子不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our box is gone
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.89,0:23:37.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:37.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
